rebounds to lead the Spartans (7-6, 2-0) to the Valley Pac-8 Conference 
victory. 
</P>
<P>
 Poly 75, Sherman Oaks CES 45 -- Darrin Drew scored a 30 points for Poly (6-4, 
1-1) in a Valley Pac-8 Conference game. WOMEN'S BASKETBALL 
</P>
<P>
 Adams State 67, The Master's 50 -- Kim DeVries had game-high totals of 19 
points and 13 rebounds, but could not prevent the Mustangs from dropping to 1-8 
in the nonconference game at Newhall. 
