INSIDE LINE: OC HIGH / STUDENT NEWS AND VIEWS; COMPLEX TREAT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 It's a question that has puzzled many: How do you eat your Reese's 
peanut-butter cup? Here's what students told the Wildcat, the newspaper at Brea 
Olinda High School: 
</P>
<P>
 * "I take tiny, tiny bits so it lasts longer." 
</P>
<P>
