APPOINTMENT OF FREEWAY FOE TO HIGHWAY POST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 What would motivate President Clinton's transportation secretary to appoint a 
professional lobbyist, outspoken on key issues, to assist the federal highway 
administrator? 
</P>
<P>
 What kind of politics is behind the recent appointment of Evelyn Fierro, a 
longtime vocal opponent to the 710 Freeway extension, to a key position within 
