<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY VIDEO RENTALS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Cynthia Kelly 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A look at the fast-moving video rentals in four Orange County neighborhoods. 
</P>
<P>
 Video 98 1235 S. Euclid Ave., Anaheim. (714) 635-4031 * Cliffhanger (Columbia 
Tri-Star) * Sliver (Paramount) * Weekend at Bernie's II (Columbia Tri-Star) * 
