<DOCNO> LA010694-0243 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 001573 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 6, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
